 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uellendilhsilvermist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ellendilh Silvermist</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://cwm.ragesofsanity.com/contrib/owen/loopy.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/17/01 5:32:40 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Black reavers nerfed or am I really unlucky?</span><hr size=1> Took about 100 reavers, spread over 6 raids and 2 months, to see my first jade reaver drop. You were saying about bad luck? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukeldenblackhawk.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kelden Blackhawk</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/17/01 5:44:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Black reavers nerfed or am I really unlucky?</span><hr size=1> Saw 2 Jade Reavers on 2 raids.  About 1/2 the reavers didn't spawn another reaver. The other 1/2 seemed to spawn at least 1 more.<br>
<br>
Both reavers dropped up top, up that walkway, in that room where the shaman named mob spawns from a Black Reaver. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=caraddor>Caraddor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(5/17/01 7:14:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Black reavers nerfed or am I really unlucky?</span><hr size=1> It took a few runs on CoM to get my jade reaver.  Not every raid will produce one.  Some raids may produce a few.  Just one of those random things.<br>
<br>
I wasn't there specifically for a jade reaver.  We were doing other epics (shaman/enchanter).  Those epics just happened to involve killing reavers.  It was a nice suprise when one dropped for me.<br>
<br>
I've been on a few trips, and I've only seen 3 jade reavers drop.<br>
<br>
Don't give up, and don't expect to get your jade reaver on your first raid.  Have fun, get exp, help others with epic stuff, and your reaver will drop soon enough.<br>
<br>
